title: Complete Web Development Bootcamp
description: Learn HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node.js, and MongoDB from scratch. Build real-world projects and become a full-stack developer.

title: Python for Data Science and Machine Learning
description: Master Python programming, data analysis with Pandas, machine learning with scikit-learn, and data visualization. Includes hands-on projects.

title: Advanced React and Redux Development
description: Deep dive into React Hooks, Redux state management, performance optimization, testing, and building production-ready applications.

title: Mobile App Development with Flutter
description: Build beautiful native mobile applications for iOS and Android using Flutter and Dart. Learn state management, APIs, and deployment.

title: DevOps Engineering: Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD
description: Master containerization with Docker, orchestration with Kubernetes, CI/CD pipelines, and infrastructure as code. Real-world DevOps projects.

title: UI/UX Design Masterclass
description: Learn user experience design, Figma, prototyping, user research, design systems, and create stunning interfaces. Portfolio projects included.

title: Cloud Computing with AWS
description: Comprehensive AWS course covering EC2, S3, Lambda, RDS, VPC, and more. Prepare for AWS Solutions Architect certification.

title: Cybersecurity Fundamentals
description: Learn network security, ethical hacking, penetration testing, cryptography, and security best practices. Hands-on labs included.

title: Digital Marketing Complete Course
description: Master SEO, social media marketing, content marketing, email campaigns, Google Ads, and analytics. Grow your business online.

title: Blockchain Development with Solidity
description: Build decentralized applications, smart contracts, DeFi protocols, and NFT marketplaces on Ethereum blockchain.

title: Game Development with Unity
description: Create 2D and 3D games using Unity engine and C#. Learn game physics, AI, animations, and publish to multiple platforms.

title: iOS App Development with Swift
description: Build native iOS applications using Swift, SwiftUI, UIKit, Core Data, and publish to the App Store. Real projects included.

title: SQL and Database Design
description: Master SQL queries, database normalization, indexing, stored procedures, and design scalable database systems.

title: Artificial Intelligence and Deep Learning
description: Learn neural networks, CNNs, RNNs, transformers, and build AI applications with TensorFlow and PyTorch. Cutting-edge projects.

title: Project Management Professional (PMP)
description: Prepare for PMP certification exam. Learn project planning, risk management, Agile, Scrum, and lead successful projects.

title: Financial Analysis and Investment
description: Learn financial modeling, valuation techniques, portfolio management, investment strategies, and Excel for finance.

title: English Speaking and Communication
description: Improve English fluency, pronunciation, business communication, presentation skills, and interview preparation.

title: Photography Masterclass
description: Master camera settings, composition, lighting, portrait photography, landscape photography, and photo editing with Lightroom and Photoshop.
